name: XBlue Finance
additional_notices: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Xblue Finance is a decentralized protocol yieldfarming and yield aggregator built on the Arbitrum network, in order to provide liquidity pools in Camelot Exchange, attracting large scale of deep liquidity and increasing attraction by the L2 ecosystem.

What makes your project unique?
Yieldfarming with use cases for the native token. (Real Yield , Dividend System)

History of your project.
We are a new project in the arbitrum network, with the objective of seeking deep liquidity for the ecosystem

What’s next for your project?
We are a new project in the arbitrum network, with the objective of seeking deep liquidity for the ecosystem

What can your token be used for?
Farm, real yield, governance.
